  ('bookkeeper-moex-00003', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-114-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'essay', '甲公司 X1 年底存貨按先進先出法計算之成本金額為$80,000，公允價值
